    "description": "<p>SECURITY & RISK SOLUTIONS PTE. LTD was founded in 2006. We started out as a provider of technical personnel for security hardware and access control systems. With our diligent and conscientious effort to fulfill our client's requirement, this gave rise to opportunities for SRS to offer wider scope of services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We, have earned the trust of our clients through close cooperation and from our efforts to understand our clients' unique security concerns. This enables us to learn more about our clients' needs & make SRS standout from other security providers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> Our Officers are experienced and equipped with skills in their respective field of expertise. Our senior management staffs are from the Police KINS unit, Security Command Unit of Singapore Police Force, United Nation Peacekeeping Unit & Special Operations Force (Counter-Terrorism Unit) from the Singapore Armed Forces.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n",
